Intro.title: Intro
Intro.description: Web3MQ is a decentralized secure communication protocol dedicated to becoming crypto-native communication infrastructure. We reconnect isolated social platforms with a unified inbox, enabling information to be freely generated, flowed and communicated across terminals. We support end-to-end encrypted communication with distributed storage, ensuring that no third party can access users' chat messages and that users have full ownership of their data.

Web3MQ-UI-Components/Web3MQ-React/chatCo.title: Channel
Web3MQ-UI-Components/Web3MQ-React/chatCo.description: The Channel component is a React Context provider that wraps all of the logic, functionality, and UI for an individual chat channel. It provides five separate contexts to its children:

Web3MQ-UI-Components/Web3MQ-React/chatCo.title: ChannelHead
Web3MQ-UI-Components/Web3MQ-React/chatCo.description: ChannelHead作为DashBoard的head部分，内部有Notifition及CreateChannel组件，需要在Chat组件中使用。

Web3MQ-UI-Components/Web3MQ-React/chatCo.title: Channel List
Web3MQ-UI-Components/Web3MQ-React/chatCo.description: The ChannelList component queries an array of channel objects from the Chat API

Web3MQ-UI-Components/Web3MQ-React/chatCo.title: CreateChannel
Web3MQ-UI-Components/Web3MQ-React/chatCo.description: CreateChannel是发送好友及创建聊天室的集功能和UI的组件，在组件内需要通过useChatContext获取client的属性，即无法在Chat组件外部单独使用。

Web3MQ-UI-Components/Web3MQ-React/chatCo.title: DashBoard
Web3MQ-UI-Components/Web3MQ-React/chatCo.description: DashBoard是一个Tabs组件。当不传入任何props时，tabs内容默认渲染组件库中ChannelList、ContactList、Profile三个组件。DashBoar组件通过useChatContext获取setShowListTypeView方法，并修改showListTypeView，即无法在Chat组件之外使用。

Web3MQ-UI-Components/Web3MQ-React/chatCo.title: MessageHead
Web3MQ-UI-Components/Web3MQ-React/chatCo.description: MessageHead是作为消息头部组件，需要作为Chat和Channel的子组件使用，从context获取activeChannel和client来渲染当前频道内容，和一些功能实现。

Web3MQ-UI-Components/Web3MQ-React/chatCo.title: MessageInput
Web3MQ-UI-Components/Web3MQ-React/chatCo.description: MessageInput本质是一个React Context Provider，没有注入任何UI；若在MessageInput中没有传入Input参数，则默认渲染我们自己Input组件样式；通过context传递给默认或自定义Input组件sendMessage的方法。

Web3MQ-UI-Components/Web3MQ-React/chatCo.title: MessageList
Web3MQ-UI-Components/Web3MQ-React/chatCo.description: The MessageList component renders a scrollable list of messages. The UI for each individual message is rendered conditionally based on its message.type value. The list renders date separators, new message notifications, system messages, deleted messages, and standard messages containing text and/or attachments.

Web3MQ-UI-Components/Web3MQ-React/chatCo.title: Notify
Web3MQ-UI-Components/Web3MQ-React/chatCo.description: Notify是给用户发送通知的功能组件，组件内功能需要基于client的api进行实现，只能在Chat中使用。

Web3MQ-UI-Components/Web3MQ-React/chatCo.title: Profile
Web3MQ-UI-Components/Web3MQ-React/chatCo.description: Profile是展示个人信息页的组件，组件内会通过ChatContext获取logout方法，需要在配合Chat使用。

Web3MQ-UI-Components/Web3MQ-React/utilit.title: Popover
Web3MQ-UI-Components/Web3MQ-React/utilit.description: 鼠标移入元素，弹出气泡式的卡片浮层。

Web3MQ-UI-Components/Web3MQ-React/utilit.title: Skeleton
Web3MQ-UI-Components/Web3MQ-React/utilit.description: Skeleton是一个在需要等待加载内容的位置提供一个占位图形组合的UI组件。

Web3MQ-UI-Components/Web3MQ-React/utilit.title: Toast
Web3MQ-UI-Components/Web3MQ-React/utilit.description: toast是在全局用于展示操作反馈信息。

Web3MQ-UI-Components/Web3MQ-React/utilit.title: Window
Web3MQ-UI-Components/Web3MQ-React/utilit.description: Window是样式组件，用于兼容视图。

Web3MQ-UI-Components/Web3MQ-Swift/Channe.description: The ChannelListViewController is the UI component used to display a list of channels matching the given query.

Web3MQ-UI-Components/Web3MQ-Vue/chatComp.title: Channel
Web3MQ-UI-Components/Web3MQ-Vue/chatComp.description: The Channel component is a Vue dependency provider that wraps all of the logic, functionality, and UI for an individual chat channel. It provides two separate Vue Provide to its children:

Web3MQ-UI-Components/Web3MQ-Vue/chatComp.title: Channel List
Web3MQ-UI-Components/Web3MQ-Vue/chatComp.description: The ChannelList component queries an array of channel objects from the Chat API, it subscribes internally to the channel.type event and updates the channel list data based on it.

Web3MQ-UI-Components/Web3MQ-Vue/chatComp.title: Message Input
Web3MQ-UI-Components/Web3MQ-Vue/chatComp.description: The MessageInput component is the method provider, such as send messages.

Web3MQ-UI-Components/Web3MQ-Vue/chatComp.title: MessageList
Web3MQ-UI-Components/Web3MQ-Vue/chatComp.description: The MessageList component renders a scrollable list of messages. The UI for each individual message is rendered conditionally based on its message.type value. The list renders standard messages.
